## PART 1 — TAGS (15 minutes)

Create these tags first. Everything else depends on them.

Go to: **Contacts → Tags → Add Tag**

Create each of the following:

| Tag Name | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `atlaabi-email-opened` | Opened any campaign email |
| `atlaabi-page-visited` | Visited AtlantaAIBusiness.com |
| `atlaabi-seat-purchased` | Confirmed event buyer — exits all drips |
| `atlaabi-webinar-registered` | Signed up for the April 28 webinar |
| `atlaabi-webinar-attended` | Attended the live webinar |
| `atlaabi-starter-kit-buyer` | Purchased the $17 Starter Kit |
| `atlaabi-vip-interest` | Clicked VIP-specific content or link |

